        <updateDate>2021-08-18T18:41:07Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Resiliency Enhancement Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill extends the provision of disaster assistance for critical services to solid waste management, stormwater management, public housing, transportation infrastructure, and medical care.</p> <p>Such assistance is also extended to any major disaster in Puerto Rico or the U.S. Virgin Islands subsequent to Hurricane Irma or Hurricane Maria on or before September 30, 2022.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
